metadata.name: Grinberg meets Dalí
metadata.description:
In the first place it’s pretty clear that we interact with an organizational matrix, a kind of informational field,
Which contains all of the information within each of its portions,  it’s a holographic type organizational matrix. 
But there is no quality of experience at that level, objects are not separated they exist 
in an extraordinary complex reality beyond our understanding

Piece inspired in the work of genious Dalí surrealism and the extraordinary mind of Jacobo Grinberg
